<section id="Creating_a_Namespace" remap="TID_41995">
	<title>Creating a Namespace</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Create a Namespace</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Automate</guimenu><guisubmenu>Explorer</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. The default view is the Datastore.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate through the various Domains and Namespaces until you reach the desired location for your new Namespace.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject><guilabel>(Configuration)</guilabel>, then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2365.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>(Add a New Namespace)</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Type in a unique <guilabel>Name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Description</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>Add</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<formalpara>
		<title>Result:</title>
		<para>
			The new Namespace is created.
		</para>
	</formalpara>
</section>